formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
The Promoter has taken Secured Loan From Bank. As it is in not in our knowledge whether encumbrance is created or not we have not reported it.
As No Separate Account is maintained we are not able to ascertain Withdrawal Amount.
In the absence of Bank Reconciliation we have considered Bank Balance as Per Books.
As Informed to us Unit No A-12 is cancelled so we have shown as Unbooked although the booking amount is yet to be refunded to allottee
We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost.The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances.The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA , and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing.Cost of Land is considered as per the sale deed of Land. Land cost is not indexed. Carpet Area of the unit, Exclusive Balcony Area of the unit, and No of parkings are taken as provided by the management. Booking Deposits received for sold inventory and consideration for unsold inventory is taken as provided by the management and as per books of accounts as mentioned under booking deposits received. Also in case of KYC/Contact Details of the allottees the same is taken as provided by the management.
